An [[Appropriation (law)|appropriation]] was approved by the city council, authorizing the city to spend $34 million from the general fund. The appropriation was recorded in fund's general ledger with a debit to ''Fund Balance'' and a credit to ''Appropriations''.<ref name="Hay 44" />

