=== Payroll expenditures ===
The city spent a total of $30 million on its employee payroll, including various taxes, benefits and employee withholding. A portion of the payroll taxes will be paid in the next fiscal period, but modified accrual accounting requires the expenditure to be recorded during the period the liability was incurred.<ref name="Hay page 8" /><ref name="Maryland page 48" />

