=== Closing entries ===
At the end of the fiscal year, the actual revenues of $36 million were compared with the estimate of $35 million. The $1 million difference was recorded as a credit to the fund balance.<ref name="Hay 77">Closing entries for a government's funds are similar to those of a for-profit business. The totals recorded in ''revenues'' and ''appropriations'' are reversed with debits while ''expenditures'' and ''estimated revenues'' are reversed with credits. The difference is applied to ''fund balance'' as a credit (surplus) or debit (deficit). Hay, p. 76-77.</ref>

